{"parse":{"title":"Entry Grade","pageid":60668,"text":{"*":"<div class=\"mw-content-ltr mw-parser-output\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><figure class=\"thumb  show-info-icon\" typeof=\"mw:File/Thumb\" style=\"width: 200px\"> \t<a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/3/32/EG_2020logo.png/revision/latest?cb=20200615095512\" class=\"mw-file-description image\"><img alt=\"Entry Grade (2020) Logo\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"200\" height=\"33\" class=\"thumbimage lazyload\" data-image-name=\"EG 2020logo.png\" data-image-key=\"EG_2020logo.png\" data-relevant=\"1\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/3/32/EG_2020logo.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/200?cb=20200615095512\" /></a> \t<noscript><a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/3/32/EG_2020logo.png/revision/latest?cb=20200615095512\" class=\"mw-file-description image\"><img alt=\"Entry Grade (2020) Logo\" src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/3/32/EG_2020logo.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/200?cb=20200615095512\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"200\" height=\"33\" class=\"thumbimage\" data-image-name=\"EG 2020logo.png\" data-image-key=\"EG_2020logo.png\" data-relevant=\"1\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/3/32/EG_2020logo.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/200?cb=20200615095512\" /></a></noscript> \t<figcaption class=\"thumbcaption\"> \t\t \t\t\t<a href=\"/wiki/File:EG_2020logo.png\" class=\"info-icon\"><svg><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-info-small\"></use></svg></a> \t\t \t\t \t\t \t\t\t<p class=\"caption\">Entry Grade (2020) Logo</p> \t\t \t</figcaption> </figure>\n<p><b>Entry Grade (EG)</b><span style=\"font-weight: normal\"> (<span class=\"t_nihongo_kanji\" lang=\"ja\">\u30a8\u30f3\u30c8\u30ea\u30fc\u30b0\u30ec\u30fc\u30c9</span><span class=\"t_nihongo_comma\" style=\"display:none\">,</span> <i><span class=\"t_nihongo_romaji\">Entor\u012b Gur\u0113do</span></i><span class=\"t_nihongo_help\"><sup><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Help:Japanese\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"wikipedia:Help:Japanese\"><span class=\"t_nihongo_icon\" style=\"color:#00e;font:bold 80% sans-serif;text-decoration:none;padding:0 .1em;\">?</span></a></sup></span>)</span> is a line of 1/144 scale <a href=\"/wiki/Gunpla\" title=\"Gunpla\">Gunpla</a> kits of the <a href=\"/wiki/Mobile_Weapon\" title=\"Mobile Weapon\">Mobile Suits</a> from the <i>Gundam</i> meta series.\n</p><p>Introduced in 2011 and made in China, the original line was marketed to emerging markets in Asia. EG kits are similar to <a href=\"/wiki/First_Grade\" title=\"First Grade\">First Grade</a> or No Grade 1/144 series Gunpla kits, wherein they contain no polycaps and are molded in only three colors. Each kit comes with a parts separator, which eliminates the need for a pair of nippers. Articulation is limited to the neck, shoulders, hips and ankles; limbs are molded in 1-3 pieces each and are hollow on one side. There is no standalone manual, instructions are printed on the backside of the box cover instead. These kits sold at under US$5.00 at toy stores, and only four models were released. In parts of Asia, these kits are given for free to customers who register with the local Bandai mailing list during special Gunpla promotional events.<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\"><span class=\"cite-bracket\">&#91;</span>1<span class=\"cite-bracket\">&#93;</span></a></sup>\n</p><p>In 2020, Bandai Spirits rebooted the Entry Grade line with kits for the <i>Kamen Rider</i>, <i>Dragon Ball</i>, <i>Doraemon</i>, <i>Ultraman</i>, <i>Pac-Man</i>, <i>My Hero Academia</i>, <i>Detective Conan</i>, and <i>Kirby</i> franchises. The new Entry Grade line features advanced color separation, articulation and proportions equivalent to most <a href=\"/wiki/High_Grade\" title=\"High Grade\">High Grade</a> kits. Similar to the 2011 releases, nipper is not needed. However, instead of using a parts separator, gates of plate runners have been redesigned such that parts can be removed by hand.\n</p><p>Following the reorganization of Bandai Namco Group, box covers of reissue and future release of kits from mid-2022 onwards feature the Bandai Namco logo on the upper right corner.\n</p><p>This article covers only the <i>Gundam</i> releases.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\" role=\"navigation\" aria-labelledby=\"mw-toc-heading\"><input type=\"checkbox\" role=\"button\" id=\"toctogglecheckbox\" class=\"toctogglecheckbox\" style=\"display:none\" /><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2 id=\"mw-toc-heading\">Contents</h2><span class=\"toctogglespan\"><label class=\"toctogglelabel\" for=\"toctogglecheckbox\"></label></span></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Entry_Grade_(2011)\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Entry Grade (2011)</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Entry_Grade_(2020)\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Entry Grade (2020)</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Exclusives\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Exclusives</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Notes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Notes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#See_also\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">See also</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#External_links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span id=\"Entry_Grade_.282011.29\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Entry_Grade_(2011)\">Entry Grade (2011)</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fgundam.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FEntry_Grade%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D1&amp;uselang=en&amp;metadata=article-registration-edit-article-section\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\" aria-label=\"Sign in to edit\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\" aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<table class=\"wikitable sortable\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th>EG #\n</th>\n<th>Model\n</th>\n<th>Series\n</th>\n<th>Release Date\n</th>\n<th>Notes\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>1 <figure class=\"mw-halign-right\" typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/5/54/Eg00.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20140109081022\" class=\"mw-file-description image\"><img alt=\"Eg00\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"130\" height=\"160\" class=\"mw-file-element lazyload\" data-image-name=\"Eg00.jpg\" data-image-key=\"Eg00.jpg\" data-relevant=\"1\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/5/54/Eg00.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/130?cb=20140109081022\" /></a><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/GN-0000_00_Gundam\" title=\"GN-0000 00 Gundam\">GN-0000 00 Gundam</a>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Mobile_Suit_Gundam_00\" title=\"Mobile Suit Gundam 00\">Mobile Suit Gundam 00</a>\n</td>\n<td>2011\n</td>\n<td>Backpack accommodates the <a href=\"/wiki/High_Grade_Gundam_00\" title=\"High Grade Gundam 00\">High Grade Gundam 00</a> <a href=\"/wiki/GNR-010_0_Raiser\" title=\"GNR-010 0 Raiser\">GNR-010 0 Raiser</a>, but the design of the kit does not allow the wing binders to attach to the GN Drives.\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>2 <figure class=\"mw-halign-right\" typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/9/90/Egexia.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20140109081019\" class=\"mw-file-description image\"><img alt=\"Egexia\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"130\" height=\"159\" class=\"mw-file-element lazyload\" data-image-name=\"Egexia.jpg\" data-image-key=\"Egexia.jpg\" data-relevant=\"1\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/9/90/Egexia.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/130?cb=20140109081019\" /></a><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/GN-001_Gundam_Exia\" title=\"GN-001 Gundam Exia\">GN-001 Gundam Exia</a>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Mobile_Suit_Gundam_00\" title=\"Mobile Suit Gundam 00\">Mobile Suit Gundam 00</a>\n</td>\n<td>2011\n</td>\n<td>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>3 <figure class=\"mw-halign-right\" typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/6/63/Egrx78.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20140109081033\" class=\"mw-file-description image\"><img alt=\"Egrx78\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"130\" height=\"159\" class=\"mw-file-element lazyload\" data-image-name=\"Egrx78.jpg\" data-image-key=\"Egrx78.jpg\" data-relevant=\"1\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/6/63/Egrx78.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/130?cb=20140109081033\" /></a><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/RX-78-2_Gundam\" title=\"RX-78-2 Gundam\">RX-78-2 Gundam</a>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Mobile_Suit_Gundam\" title=\"Mobile Suit Gundam\">Mobile Suit Gundam</a>\n</td>\n<td>2011\n</td>\n<td>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>4 <figure class=\"mw-halign-right\" typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/6/63/Egstrike.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20140109081029\" class=\"mw-file-description image\"><img alt=\"Egstrike\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"130\" height=\"159\" class=\"mw-file-element lazyload\" data-image-name=\"Egstrike.jpg\" data-image-key=\"Egstrike.jpg\" data-relevant=\"1\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/6/63/Egstrike.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/130?cb=20140109081029\" /></a><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/GAT-X105_Strike_Gundam\" title=\"GAT-X105 Strike Gundam\">GAT-X105 Strike Gundam</a>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Mobile_Suit_Gundam_SEED\" title=\"Mobile Suit Gundam SEED\">Mobile Suit Gundam SEED</a>\n</td>\n<td>2011\n</td>\n<td>Compatible with <a href=\"/wiki/1/144_Gundam_SEED_Model_Series\" title=\"1/144 Gundam SEED Model Series\">No Grade</a> and <a href=\"/wiki/High_Grade_Gundam_SEED\" title=\"High Grade Gundam SEED\">High Grade Gundam SEED</a> Striker Packs.\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>Yen price excluding 5% tax (8% from 2014 to 2019; 10% from 2019 October onwards).\n</p>\n<h2><span id=\"Entry_Grade_.282020.29\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Entry_Grade_(2020)\">Entry Grade (2020)</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fgundam.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FEntry_Grade%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D2&amp;uselang=en&amp;metadata=article-registration-edit-article-section\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\" aria-label=\"Sign in to edit\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\" aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"tabber wds-tabber\"><div class=\"wds-tabs__wrapper with-bottom-border\"><ul class=\"wds-tabs\"><li class=\"wds-tabs__tab wds-is-current\" data-hash=\"Regular\"><div class=\"wds-tabs__tab-label\"><a href=\"#\">Regular</a></div></li><li class=\"wds-tabs__tab\" data-hash=\"Special_Editions\"><div class=\"wds-tabs__tab-label\"><a href=\"#\">Special Editions</a></div></li></ul></div><div class=\"wds-tab__content wds-is-current\"><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\">\n</p><table class=\"wikitable sortable\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th>EG #\n</th>\n<th>Model\n</th>\n<th>Series\n</th>\n<th>Yen Price\n</th>\n<th>Release Date\n</th>\n<th>Notes\n</th>\n<th>Link\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>1 <figure class=\"mw-halign-right\" typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/2/21/EG_Gundam.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20200902090519\" class=\"mw-file-description image\"><img alt=\"EG Gundam\" src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/2/21/EG_Gundam.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/130?cb=20200902090519\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"130\" height=\"171\" class=\"mw-file-element\" data-image-name=\"EG Gundam.jpg\" data-image-key=\"EG_Gundam.jpg\" data-relevant=\"1\" /></a><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/RX-78-2_Gundam\" title=\"RX-78-2 Gundam\">RX-78-2 Gundam</a>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Mobile_Suit_Gundam\" title=\"Mobile Suit Gundam\">Mobile Suit Gundam</a>\n</td>\n<td>\u00a5700\n</td>\n<td>2020 September (<a href=\"/wiki/The_Gundam_Base_Tokyo\" title=\"The Gundam Base Tokyo\">The Gundam Base Tokyo</a>) / 2021 May (Regular)\n</td>\n<td>\n</td>\n<td><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://manual.bandai-hobby.net/menus/detail/977\">Manual</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>2 <figure class=\"mw-halign-right\" typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/0/0c/EG_Strike_Gundam.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20220111132606\" class=\"mw-file-description image\"><img alt=\"EG Strike Gundam\" src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/0/0c/EG_Strike_Gundam.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/130?cb=20220111132606\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"130\" height=\"172\" class=\"mw-file-element\" data-image-name=\"EG Strike Gundam.jpg\" data-image-key=\"EG_Strike_Gundam.jpg\" data-relevant=\"1\" /></a><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/GAT-X105_Strike_Gundam\" title=\"GAT-X105 Strike Gundam\">GAT-X105 Strike Gundam</a>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Mobile_Suit_Gundam_SEED\" title=\"Mobile Suit Gundam SEED\">Mobile Suit Gundam SEED</a>\n</td>\n<td>\u00a5700\n</td>\n<td>2022 January\n</td>\n<td>Re-release of EG GAT-X105 Strike Gundam (Lite Package Ver.) with weapons. <a href=\"/wiki/GAT-X105%2BAQM/E-X01_Aile_Strike_Gundam\" title=\"GAT-X105+AQM/E-X01 Aile Strike Gundam\">Aile Striker</a>, <a href=\"/wiki/GAT-X105%2BAQM/E-X03_Launcher_Strike_Gundam\" title=\"GAT-X105+AQM/E-X03 Launcher Strike Gundam\">Launcher Striker</a>, <a href=\"/wiki/GAT-X105%2BAQM/E-X02_Sword_Strike_Gundam\" title=\"GAT-X105+AQM/E-X02 Sword Strike Gundam\">Sword Striker</a> and <a href=\"/wiki/AQM/E-X04_Gunbarrel_Striker\" title=\"AQM/E-X04 Gunbarrel Striker\">Gunbarrel Striker</a> are sold separately as <a href=\"/wiki/Option_Parts_Set\" title=\"Option Parts Set\">OPS</a>-01, OPS-02 and OPS-14 respectively. Also compatible with Aile Striker from HGCE-171.\n</td>\n<td><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://manual.bandai-hobby.net/menus/detail/980\">Manual</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>3 <figure class=\"mw-halign-right\" typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/1/1e/EG_%CE%BD_Gundam.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20220511004111\" class=\"mw-file-description image\"><img alt=\"EG \u03bd Gundam\" src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/1/1e/EG_%CE%BD_Gundam.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/130?cb=20220511004111\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"130\" height=\"82\" class=\"mw-file-element\" data-image-name=\"EG \u03bd Gundam.jpg\" data-image-key=\"EG_%CE%BD_Gundam.jpg\" data-relevant=\"1\" /></a><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/RX-93_%CE%BD_Gundam\" title=\"RX-93 \u03bd Gundam\">RX-93 \u03bd Gundam</a>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Mobile_Suit_Gundam:_Char%27s_Counterattack\" title=\"Mobile Suit Gundam: Char&#39;s Counterattack\">Mobile Suit Gundam: Char's Counterattack</a>\n</td>\n<td>\u00a51,000\n</td>\n<td>2022 April\n</td>\n<td>Fin Funnels are sold separately as OPS-19. Also compatible with Fin Funnels, Nu Hyper Bazooka, and Beam Saber effect parts from HGUC-086.\n</td>\n<td><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://manual.bandai-hobby.net/menus/detail/1051\">Manual</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>4 <figure class=\"mw-halign-right\" typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/d/da/EG_Strike_Rouge.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20250115005140\" class=\"mw-file-description image\"><img alt=\"EG Strike Rouge\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"130\" height=\"172\" class=\"mw-file-element lazyload\" data-image-name=\"EG Strike Rouge.jpg\" data-image-key=\"EG_Strike_Rouge.jpg\" data-relevant=\"1\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/d/da/EG_Strike_Rouge.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/130?cb=20250115005140\" /></a><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/MBF-02_Strike_Rouge\" title=\"MBF-02 Strike Rouge\">MBF-02 Strike Rouge</a>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Mobile_Suit_Gundam_SEED\" title=\"Mobile Suit Gundam SEED\">Mobile Suit Gundam SEED</a>\n</td>\n<td>\u00a5800\n</td>\n<td>2025 January\n</td>\n<td>Re-release of EG Round Box with Gunpla MBF-02 Strike Rouge (Armor Schneider Equipped) with Beam Rifle instead of Armor Schneiders. <a href=\"/wiki/MBF-02%2BAQM/E-X01_Aile_Strike_Rouge\" title=\"MBF-02+AQM/E-X01 Aile Strike Rouge\">Aile Striker</a> and <a href=\"/wiki/AMGS-X18P_Cavalier_Aifrid\" title=\"AMGS-X18P Cavalier Aifrid\">AMGS-X18P Cavalier Aifrid</a> are sold separately as OPS-1 and OPS-15 respectively. Also compatible with Aile Striker from HGCE-176.\n</td>\n<td><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://manual.bandai-hobby.net/menus/detail/2082\">Manual</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>5 <figure class=\"mw-halign-right\" typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/8/83/EG_Wing_Gundam.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20251104090537\" class=\"mw-file-description image\"><img alt=\"EG Wing Gundam\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"130\" height=\"82\" class=\"mw-file-element lazyload\" data-image-name=\"EG Wing Gundam.jpg\" data-image-key=\"EG_Wing_Gundam.jpg\" data-relevant=\"1\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/8/83/EG_Wing_Gundam.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/130?cb=20251104090537\" /></a><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/XXXG-01W_Wing_Gundam\" title=\"XXXG-01W Wing Gundam\">XXXG-01W Wing Gundam</a>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Mobile_Suit_Gundam_Wing\" title=\"Mobile Suit Gundam Wing\">Mobile Suit Gundam Wing</a>\n</td>\n<td>\u00a51,000\n</td>\n<td>2025 August (US)<br />2025 October (Japan)\n</td>\n<td>Released to commemorate the 30th anniversary of <i>Gundam Wing</i>. Although not stated in the instruction manual, it can transform into a Bird Mode-like state, with the claws unable to deploy fully and the knees and feet unable to bend/fold fully.\n</td>\n<td>\n</td></tr></tbod