%3D\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"130\" height=\"98\" class=\"mw-file-element lazyload\" data-image-name=\"EG Gundam (Full Weapon Set).jpg\" data-image-key=\"EG_Gundam_%28Full_Weapon_Set%29.jpg\" data-relevant=\"1\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/c/c0/EG_Gundam_%28Full_Weapon_Set%29.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/130?cb=20211201091408\" /></a><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/RX-78-2_Gundam\" title=\"RX-78-2 Gundam\">RX-78-2 Gundam</a> (Full Weapon Set)\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Mobile_Suit_Gundam\" title=\"Mobile Suit Gundam\">Mobile Suit Gundam</a>\n</td>\n<td>\u00a51.000\n</td>\n<td>2021 December\n</td>\n<td>Re-release of EG-1 with Beam Saber, Hyper Bazooka, Beam Javelin and Gundam Hammer.\n</td>\n<td><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://manual.bandai-hobby.net/menus/detail/979\">Manual</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>N/A\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/GAT-X105_Strike_Gundam\" title=\"GAT-X105 Strike Gundam\">GAT-X105 Strike Gundam</a> (Lite Package Ver.)\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Mobile_Suit_Gundam_SEED\" title=\"Mobile Suit Gundam SEED\">Mobile Suit Gundam SEED</a>\n</td>\n<td>\u00a5500\n</td>\n<td>2021 December\n</td>\n<td>Re-release of EG GAT-X105 Strike Gundam Solid Clear without clear color armor parts. Package uses PP bag instead of box.\n</td>\n<td><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://manual.bandai-hobby.net/menus/detail/1050\">Manual</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>N/A\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/GAT-X105_Strike_Gundam\" title=\"GAT-X105 Strike Gundam\">GAT-X105 Strike Gundam</a> (Deactive Mode)\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Mobile_Suit_Gundam_SEED\" title=\"Mobile Suit Gundam SEED\">Mobile Suit Gundam SEED</a>\n</td>\n<td>\u00a51,400\n</td>\n<td>2022 July\n</td>\n<td>Color variant of EG-2. Includes two Bikkura Tamago bath bombs containing <a href=\"/wiki/UMF-4A_GOOhN\" title=\"UMF-4A GOOhN\">UMF-4A GOOhN</a> (Sand Yellow) and <a href=\"/wiki/UMF-5_ZnO\" title=\"UMF-5 ZnO\">UMF-5 ZnO</a> (Light Gray) Mini Gunpla kits.\n</td>\n<td>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>N/A\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/GAT-X105_Strike_Gundam\" title=\"GAT-X105 Strike Gundam\">GAT-X105 Strike Gundam</a> (Grand Slam Equipped Type)\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Mobile_Suit_Gundam_SEED\" title=\"Mobile Suit Gundam SEED\">Mobile Suit Gundam SEED</a>\n</td>\n<td>\u00a51,400\n</td>\n<td>2022 July\n</td>\n<td>Re-release of EG-2 with Grand Slam. Includes two Bikkura Tamago bath bombs containing UMF-4A GOOhN (Brown) and UMF-5 ZnO (Green) Mini Gunpla kits.\n</td>\n<td>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>N/A\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/GAT-X105%2BAQM/E-X04_Gunbarrel_Strike_Gundam\" title=\"GAT-X105+AQM/E-X04 Gunbarrel Strike Gundam\">GAT-X105+AQM/E-X04 Gunbarrel Strike Gundam</a> (Gundam Breaker Ver.)\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Gundam_Breaker_4\" title=\"Gundam Breaker 4\">Gundam Breaker 4</a>\n</td>\n<td>\u00a518,500\n</td>\n<td>2024 August\n</td>\n<td>Limited edition parts and color variant of EG-2; bundled with <i>Gundam Break 4 Collector Edition</i>.\n</td>\n<td>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>N/A <figure class=\"mw-halign-right\" typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/b/be/EG_RX-78F00_E_Gundam.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20250723160148\" class=\"mw-file-description image\"><img alt=\"EG RX-78F00 E Gundam\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"130\" height=\"172\" class=\"mw-file-element lazyload\" data-image-name=\"EG RX-78F00 E Gundam.jpg\" data-image-key=\"EG_RX-78F00_E_Gundam.jpg\" data-relevant=\"1\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/b/be/EG_RX-78F00_E_Gundam.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/130?cb=20250723160148\" /></a><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/RX-78F00/E_Gundam\" title=\"RX-78F00/E 