ata-relevant=\"1\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/e/ea/EG_Nu_Gundam_Luminescent_Psycho-Frame_Image_Color.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/130?cb=20240607031633\" /></a><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n</td>\n<td>Carrying Box with Gunpla <a href=\"/wiki/RX-93_%CE%BD_Gundam\" title=\"RX-93 \u03bd Gundam\">RX-93 \u03bd Gundam</a> (Luminescent Psycho-Frame Image Color)\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Mobile_Suit_Gundam:_Char%27s_Counterattack\" title=\"Mobile Suit Gundam: Char&#39;s Counterattack\">Mobile Suit Gundam: Char's Counterattack</a>\n</td>\n<td>\u00a51,600\n</td>\n<td>2024 October\n</td>\n<td>HEART Co. Ltd/Rakuten exclusive color variant of EG-3 bundled with one bag of cider ramune candies. Uses paper package instead of box.\n</td></tr></tbody></table><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p></div><div class=\"wds-tab__content\"><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\">\n</p><table class=\"wikitable sortable\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th>EG #\n</th>\n<th>Model\n</th>\n<th>Series\n</th>\n<th>Yen Price\n</th>\n<th>Release Date\n</th>\n<th>Notes\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>N/A\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/RX-93_%CE%BD_Gundam\" title=\"RX-93 \u03bd Gundam\">RX-93 \u03bd Gundam</a> (Axis Shock Image Color)\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Mobile_Suit_Gundam:_Char%27s_Counterattack\" title=\"Mobile Suit Gundam: Char&#39;s Counterattack\">Mobile Suit Gundam: Char's Counterattack</a>\n</td>\n<td>\u00a51,400\n</td>\n<td>2025 July\n</td>\n<td>Gundam Side-F exclusive color variant of EG-3.\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>N/A\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/RX-78-2_Gundam\" title=\"RX-78-2 Gundam\">RX-78-2 Gundam</a> (Full Weapon Set) [BHCPDII Color]\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Mobile_Suit_Gundam\" title=\"Mobile Suit Gundam\">Mobile Suit Gundam</a>\n</td>\n<td>\u00a51,300\n</td>\n<td>2025 September\n</td>\n<td>Bandai Hobby Center Plamo Design Industrial Institute Museum exclusive color variant of EG RX-78-2 Gundam (Full Weapon Set).\n</td></tr></tbody></table><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p></div></div><p>Yen price excluding 10% tax.\n</p><h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Notes\">Notes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fgundam.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FEntry_Grade%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D4&amp;uselang=en&amp;metadata=article-registration-edit-article-section\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\" aria-label=\"Sign in to edit\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\" aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li>EG kits bundled with Mini Gunpla use the red Bandai logo instead of the new blue logo, indicating they are released under the original Bandai, instead of the new Bandai Spirits like other gunpla kits following the reorganization of Bandai Namco Group.</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fgundam.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FEntry_Grade%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D5&amp;uselang=en&amp;metadata=article-registration-edit-article-section\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\" aria-label=\"Sign in to edit\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\" aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Option_Parts_Set\" title=\"Option Parts Set\">Option Parts Set</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/First_Grade\" title=\"First Grade\">First Grade</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Advanced_Grade\" title=\"Advanced Grade\">Advanced Grade</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/High_Grade\" title=\"High Grade\">High Grade</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/High_Grade_Gundam_Build_Metaverse\" title=\"High Grade Gundam Build Metaverse\">High Grade Gundam Build Metaverse</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/The_Gundam_Base_Tokyo\" title=\"The Gundam Base Tokyo\">The Gundam Base Tokyo</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Gundam_Side-F\" title=\"Gundam Side-F\">Gundam Side-F</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Gundam_Next_Future_Pavilion\" title=\"Gundam Next Future Pavilion\">Gundam Next Future Pavilion</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_links\">External links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fgundam.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FEntry_Grade%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D6&amp;uselang=en&amp;metadata=article-registration-edit-article-section\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\" aria-label=\"Sign in to edit\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\" aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://bandai-hobby.net/brand/entry_grade_g/\">Bandai Hobby Site's Official Entry Grade Site</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fgundam.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FEntry_Grade%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D7&